#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:2
msgid "网络攻防技术演化"
msgstr "Evolution of Network Attack and Defense Technologies"

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:5
msgid "历史发展"
msgstr "Historical Development"

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:6
msgid "1939年，图灵破解了Enigma，使战争提前结束了两年，这是较早的一次计算机安全开始出现在人们的视野中，这个时候计算机的算力有限，人们使用的攻防方式也相对初级。"
msgstr "In 1939, Turing broke Enigma, helping end the war two years earlier. This was one of the early moments when computer security began to enter public view. At that time, computing power was limited, and attack and defense methods were relatively basic."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:8
msgid "1949年，约翰·冯·诺依曼（John Von Neumann）提出了一种可自我复制的程序的设计，这被认为是世界上第一种计算机病毒。"
msgstr "In 1949, John von Neumann proposed the design of a self-replicating program, which is regarded as the world's first computer virus concept."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:10
msgid "1970年到2009年间，随着因特网不断发展，网络安全也开始进入人们的视野。在网络发展的初期，很多系统都是零防护的，安全意识也尚未普及开来。很多系统的设计也只考虑了可用性，对安全性的考虑不多，所以在当时结合搜索引擎与一些集成渗透测试工具，可以很容易的拿到数据或者权限。"
msgstr "From 1970 to 2009, as the Internet continued to develop, network security also entered public view. In the early stages of network development, many systems had no protection at all, and security awareness was not yet widespread. Many systems were designed mainly for usability with little consideration for security, so at the time it was often easy to obtain data or privileges by combining search engines with integrated penetration testing tools."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:12
msgid "1972年，缓冲区溢出攻击被 Computer Security Technology Planning Study 提出。"
msgstr "In 1972, buffer overflow attacks were described in the Computer Security Technology Planning Study."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:14
msgid ""
"1984年，Ken Thompson 在 Reflections on Trusting Trust 一文中介绍了自己如何在编译器中增加后门来获取"
" Unix 权限的，这也是较早的供应链攻击。"
msgstr ""
"In 1984, Ken Thompson described in Reflections on Trusting Trust how he added a backdoor to a compiler to obtain "
"Unix privileges. This was also an early supply chain attack."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:16
msgid ""
"1988年，卡耐基梅隆大学(Carnegie Mellon University, CMU)的一位学生以测试的目的编写了Morris "
"Worm，对当时的互联网造成了极大的损害。"
msgstr ""
"In 1988, a student at Carnegie Mellon University (CMU) wrote the Morris "
"Worm for testing purposes, causing major damage to the Internet at the time."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:18
msgid ""
"同年，CMU的CERT Coordination Center (CERT-CC)为了处理Morris "
"Worm对互联网造成的破坏，组成了第一个计算机紧急响应小组(Computer Emergency Response "
"Team)，而后全球多个国家、地区、团体都构建了CERT、SRC等组织。"
msgstr ""
"In the same year, CMU's CERT Coordination Center (CERT-CC) formed the first Computer Emergency Response "
"Team to handle the damage caused by the Morris Worm. Later, many countries, regions, and organizations around the world established CERTs, SRCs, and similar organizations."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:20
msgid ""
"同样是在1988年，Barton Miller教授在威斯康星大学的 `计算机实验课上 "
"<http://pages.cs.wisc.edu/~bart/fuzz/CS736-Projects-f1988.pdf>`_ "
"，首次提出Fuzz生成器(Fuzz Generator)的概念，用于测试Unix程序的健壮性，即用随机数据来测试程序直至崩溃。因此，Barton "
"Miller教授也被多数人尊称为\"模糊测试之父\"。"
msgstr ""
"Also in 1988, Professor Barton Miller first proposed the concept of a Fuzz Generator in a `computer lab course at the University of Wisconsin "
"<http://pages.cs.wisc.edu/~bart/fuzz/CS736-Projects-f1988.pdf>`_. "
"It was used to test the robustness of Unix programs by feeding random data to programs until they crashed. For this reason, Professor Barton "
"Miller is widely respected as the \"father of fuzz testing.\""

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:22
msgid ""
"1989年，C.J.Cherryh 发表了小说 The Cuckoo's Egg: Tracking a Spy Through the Maze"
" of Computer Espionage ，这本书是作者根据追溯黑客攻击的真实经历改编，在书中提出了蜜罐技术的雏形。"
msgstr ""
"In 1989, C. J. Cherryh published the novel The Cuckoo's Egg: Tracking a Spy Through the Maze "
"of Computer Espionage. Based on the author's real experience tracing hacker attacks, the book presented an early form of honeypot technology."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:24
msgid "1990年，一些网络防火墙的产品开始出现，此时主要是基于网络的防火墙，可以处理FTP等应用程序。"
msgstr "In 1990, some network firewall products began to appear. These were mainly network-based firewalls and could handle applications such as FTP."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:26
msgid ""
"1993年起，Jeff Moss开始每年在美国内华达州的拉斯维加斯举办 DEFCON (也写做 DEF CON, Defcon, or DC, "
"全球最大的计算机安全会议之一) 。CTF (Capture The Flag) 比赛的形式也是起源于1996年的 DEFCON 。"
msgstr ""
"Starting in 1993, Jeff Moss began holding DEFCON annually in Las Vegas, Nevada, USA (also written as DEF CON, Defcon, or DC), "
"one of the world's largest computer security conferences. The CTF (Capture The Flag) competition format also originated at DEFCON in 1996."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:28
msgid ""
"1993年7月，Windows NT 3.1发布，引入了身份认证、访问控制和安全审计等安全控制机制，在此之前的 Windows 9x "
"内核几乎没有任何安全性机制。"
msgstr ""
"In July 1993, Windows NT 3.1 was released, introducing security controls such as identity authentication, access control, and security auditing. Before this, the Windows 9x "
"kernel had almost no security mechanisms."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:30
msgid "1996年，Smashing the Stack For Fun and Profit发表，在堆栈的缓冲区溢出的利用方式上做出了开创性的工作。"
msgstr "In 1996, Smashing the Stack For Fun and Profit was published, doing pioneering work on exploiting stack-based buffer overflows."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:32
msgid ""
"1997年起，Jeff Moss开始举办 Black Hat ，以中立的立场进行信息安全研究的交流和培训，到目前为止，Black Hat "
"也会在欧洲和亚洲举行。"
msgstr ""
"Starting in 1997, Jeff Moss began organizing Black Hat as a neutral forum for information security research exchange and training. Today, Black Hat "
"is also held in Europe and Asia."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:34
msgid ""
"1998年12月，Jeff Forristal在一篇 `文章 "
"<http://www.phrack.com/issues.html?issue=54&id=8>`_ "
"中提到了使用SQL注入的技巧攻击一个网站的例子，从此SQL注入开始被广泛讨论。"
msgstr ""
"In December 1998, Jeff Forristal mentioned an example of attacking a website with SQL injection techniques in an `article "
"<http://www.phrack.com/issues.html?issue=54&id=8>`_. "
"From then on, SQL injection began to be widely discussed."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:36
msgid ""
"1999年1月21日-22日的第二届 Research with Security Vulnerability Databases 的 "
"WorkShop 上， MITRE 的创始人 David E. Mann 和 Steven M. Christey 发表了一篇名为《Towards"
" a Common Enumeration of Vulnerabilities》的白皮书，提出了CVE (Common "
"Vulnerabilities and Exposures, 通用漏洞披露) 的概念，在当年收录并公开了321个CVE漏洞。"
msgstr ""
"At the second Research with Security Vulnerability Databases "
"Workshop on January 21-22, 1999, MITRE's David E. Mann and Steven M. Christey published a white paper titled Towards "
"a Common Enumeration of Vulnerabilities. It introduced the concept of CVE (Common "
"Vulnerabilities and Exposures), and 321 CVE vulnerabilities were collected and published that year."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:38
msgid ""
"1999年12月，MSRC的一些工程师发现了一些网站被注入代码的例子，他们在整理讨论后公开了这种攻击，并称为 Cross Site "
"Scripting。"
msgstr ""
"In December 1999, some MSRC engineers discovered examples of code being injected into websites. After organizing and discussing their findings, they publicly described the attack and called it Cross Site "
"Scripting."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:40
msgid ""
"2002年1月，Microsoft发起了 “可信赖计算” (Trustworthy Computing) "
"计划，以帮助确保产品和服务在本质上具有高度安全性，可用性，可靠性以及业务完整性，SDL (Security Development "
"Lifecycle) 也在此时被提出。"
msgstr ""
"In January 2002, Microsoft launched the Trustworthy Computing "
"initiative to help ensure that products and services were inherently highly secure, available, reliable, and business-integrity focused. SDL (Security Development "
"Lifecycle) was also proposed at this time."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:42
msgid ""
"2001年9月9日，Mark Curphey启动了OWASP (Open Web Application Security Project) "
"项目，开始在社区中提供一些Web攻击技术的文章、方法和工具等。"
msgstr ""
"On September 9, 2001, Mark Curphey launched OWASP (Open Web Application Security Project), "
"which began providing articles, methods, tools, and other community resources on web attack techniques."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:44
msgid "在此之后，Responsible disclosure / Full disclosure 等概念也不断进入人们的视野之中。"
msgstr "After this, concepts such as responsible disclosure and full disclosure also increasingly entered public view."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:46
msgid ""
"2002年10月4日，Kevin Mitnick 编著的 The Art of Deception (欺骗的艺术) "
"出版，这本书详细的介绍了社会工程学在攻击中是如何应用的，Kevin Mitnick 也被认为是社会工程学的开山鼻祖。"
msgstr ""
"On October 4, 2002, The Art of Deception, written by Kevin Mitnick, "
"was published. The book explains in detail how social engineering is applied in attacks, and Kevin Mitnick is also regarded as a pioneer of social engineering."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:48
msgid "2005年7月25日，Zero Day Initiative (ZDI) 创建，鼓励负责任的漏洞披露。"
msgstr "On July 25, 2005, the Zero Day Initiative (ZDI) was created to encourage responsible vulnerability disclosure."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:50
msgid ""
"2005年11月，基于从1941年2月开始的情报收集积累和发展，Director of National Intelligence 宣布成立 "
"Open Source Center (OSC) ，进行开源情报的收集，而后 Open-source intelligence (OSINT) "
"的概念也不断被人们认知。"
msgstr ""
"In November 2005, based on intelligence collection that had accumulated and developed since February 1941, the Director of National Intelligence announced the establishment of the "
"Open Source Center (OSC) to collect open-source intelligence. Later, the concept of open-source intelligence (OSINT) "
"became increasingly recognized."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:52
msgid ""
"2006年，APT(Advanced Persistent Threat, 高级持续威胁) "
"攻击的概念被正式提出，用来描述从20世纪90年代末到21世纪初在美国军事和政府网络中发现的隐蔽且持续的网络攻击。"
msgstr ""
"In 2006, the concept of APT (Advanced Persistent Threat) "
"attacks was formally proposed to describe stealthy and persistent cyberattacks found in U.S. military and government networks from the late 1990s to the early 2000s."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:54
msgid "2006年起，美国国土安全部（DHS）开始每两年举行一次 “网络风暴” (Cyber Storm) 系列国家级网络事件演习。"
msgstr "Starting in 2006, the U.S. Department of Homeland Security (DHS) began holding the national-level Cyber Storm series of cyber incident exercises every two years."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:56
msgid "随着时代不断的发展，攻防技术有了很大的改变，防御手段、安全意识也随着演化。在攻击发生前有威胁情报、黑名单共享等机制，威胁及时能传播。在攻击发生时有基于各种机制的防火墙如关键字检测、语义分析、深度学习，有的防御机制甚至能一定程度上防御零日攻击。在攻击发生后，一些关键系统系统做了隔离，攻击成果难以扩大，就算拿到了目标也很难做进一步的攻击。也有的目标蜜罐仿真程度很高，有正常的服务和一些难以判断真假的业务数据。"
msgstr "As the times have developed, attack and defense technologies have changed greatly, and defensive measures and security awareness have evolved as well. Before attacks occur, mechanisms such as threat intelligence and blacklist sharing allow threats to be propagated quickly. During attacks, firewalls based on mechanisms such as keyword detection, semantic analysis, and deep learning are available, and some defenses can even resist zero-day attacks to a certain extent. After attacks occur, some critical systems are isolated, making it difficult to expand the impact; even if a target is compromised, further attacks may be hard to carry out. Some target honeypots are also highly realistic, with normal services and business data that are hard to distinguish from real data."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:58
msgid ""
"2010年6月，震网 (Stuxnet) "
"被发现，在这之后供应链攻击事件开始成为网络空间安全的新兴威胁之一。随后的XcodeGhost、CCleaner等供应链攻击事件都造成了重大影响。"
msgstr ""
"In June 2010, Stuxnet "
"was discovered. After this, supply chain attacks began to become one of the emerging threats in cyberspace security. Subsequent supply chain incidents such as XcodeGhost and CCleaner also had major impact."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:60
msgid "在2010年Forrester Research Inc.的分析师提出了“零信任”的概念模型时。"
msgstr "In 2010, analysts at Forrester Research Inc. proposed the Zero Trust conceptual model."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:62
msgid ""
"2012年1月，Gartner 公司提出了 IAST (Interactive Application Security Testing) "
"的概念，提供了结合 DAST 和 SAST 两种技术的解决方案。这种方式漏洞检出率高、误报率低，同时可以定位到API接口和代码片段。"
msgstr ""
"In January 2012, Gartner introduced the concept of IAST (Interactive Application Security Testing), "
"providing a solution that combines DAST and SAST. This approach has a high vulnerability detection rate and a low false-positive rate, and can also locate API interfaces and code snippets."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:64
msgid ""
"2012年9月，Gartner 公司研究员 David Cearley 提出了 DevSecOps 的概念，表示 DevOps "
"的流程应该包含安全理念。"
msgstr ""
"In September 2012, Gartner researcher David Cearley proposed the concept of DevSecOps, indicating that DevOps "
"processes should include security concepts."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:66
msgid ""
"2013年，MITRE 提出了 ATT&CK™ (Adversarial Tactics, Techniques, and Common "
"Knowledge, ATT&CK) ，这是一个站在攻击者的视角来描述攻击中各阶段用到的技术的模型。"
msgstr ""
"In 2013, MITRE proposed ATT&CK(TM) (Adversarial Tactics, Techniques, and Common "
"Knowledge), a model that describes techniques used at each stage of an attack from the attacker's perspective."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:68
msgid "2013年，Michigan 大学开始了 ZMap 项目，在2015年这个项目演化为 Censys ，从这之后网络空间测绘的项目逐渐出现。"
msgstr "In 2013, the University of Michigan started the ZMap project. In 2015, this project evolved into Censys, after which cyberspace mapping projects gradually appeared."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:70
msgid ""
"2014年，在 Gartner Security and Risk Management Summit 上，Runtime Application"
" Self-protection (RASP) 的概念被提出，在应用层进行安全保护。"
msgstr ""
"In 2014, at the Gartner Security and Risk Management Summit, the concept of Runtime Application "
"Self-protection (RASP) was introduced to provide security protection at the application layer."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:72
msgid ""
"2015年，Gartner 首次提出了 SOAR 的概念，最初的定义是 Security Operations, Analytics and "
"Reporting，即安全运维分析与报告。"
msgstr ""
"In 2015, Gartner first proposed the concept of SOAR. Its original definition was Security Operations, Analytics and "
"Reporting."

#: ../../source/basic/atkhistory.rst:74
msgid ""
"2017年，Gartner 对 SOAR 概念做了重新定义：Security Orchestration, Automation and "
"Response, 即安全编排、自动化与响应。"
msgstr ""
"In 2017, Gartner redefined SOAR as Security Orchestration, Automation and "
"Response."

